  <num>19-1702.06</num>
  <heading proof="needed">Power to revoke or amend.</heading>
  <para>
    <num undesignated="true">(a)</num>
    <text>A donor may revoke or amend a power of appointment only to the extent that:</text>
    <para>
      <num>(1)</num>
      <text>The instrument creating the power is revocable by the donor; or</text>
    </para>
    <para>
      <num>(2)</num>
      <text>The donor reserves a power of revocation or amendment in the instrument creating the power of appointment.</text>
    </para>
  </para>
